---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Fahran Gérondal | Portfolio
description: Portfolio de Fahran Gérondal, développeur web, mobile et applicatif orienté sécurité, backend, tests logiciel et conception.
pageKey: home
mainClass: page-shell home-shell reveal
permalink: /index.html
---
<section class="hero-layout">
  <section class="hero-content" data-reveal>
    <p class="eyebrow typewriter" aria-label="Spécialités">
      <span id="typewriter-text"></span><span class="cursor" aria-hidden="true">|</span>
    </p>

    <h1 class="hero-title" data-scramble>Je code, je teste, je sécurise.</h1>

    <p class="hero-text">
      Backend Node.js / TypeScript, interfaces web, bases de données, tests logiciel, sécurité applicative et conception. Je construis des solutions utiles, solides et assez claires pour rester maintenables après la livraison.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="btn primary magnetic" href="{{ '/projets.html' | url }}"><span>Voir mes projets</span></a>
      <a class="btn ghost magnetic" href="{{ '/formations.html' | url }}"><span>Mes certifications</span></a>
    </div>

    <section class="cert-strip" aria-label="Certifications ISTQB clés">
      {% for certification in certifications %}
        <article class="cert-pill" data-cert-pulse data-reveal>
          <span>ISTQB</span>
          <strong>{{ certification.homeTitle }}</strong>
          <small>{{ certification.shortDescription }}</small>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </section>

    <section class="stats-grid" aria-label="Résumé chiffré">
      {% for stat in statistics.home %}
        {% include "components/stat-card.njk" %}
      {% endfor %}
    </section>
  </section>

  <aside class="hero-card glass-card tilt-card" aria-label="Résumé professionnel" data-reveal>
    <div class="status-dot">Disponible pour opportunités</div>

    <div class="hero-card-top">
      <span>QA-ready</span>
      <span>Backend-first</span>
    </div>

    <h2>Fahran Gérondal</h2>
    <p>Développeur orienté qualité, sécurité, backend et conception applicative.</p>

    <div class="quality-meter" aria-label="Mise en avant certifications ISTQB">
      <div>
        <span>Certifications qualité</span>
        <strong>ISTQB x3</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="meter-track" aria-hidden="true"><span></span></div>
    </div>

    <ul class="quick-list">
      <li>
        <strong>Stack forte</strong>
        <span>Node.js, TypeScript, Express, Sequelize</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Applicatif</strong>
        <span>C#, WPF, C++, Qt Creator</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Qualité</strong>
        <span>Cas de test, anomalies, critères d'acceptation</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </aside>
</section>

<section class="cert-showcase" aria-label="Certifications ISTQB" data-reveal>
  <div class="section-heading compact">
    <p class="eyebrow">Triple certification ISTQB</p>
    <h2>Un profil dev qui parle aussi test, risque et qualité livrable.</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="certification-grid">
    {% for certification in certifications %}
      {% set index = loop.index %}
      {% set summary = certification.summary %}
      {% set headingLevel = 3 %}
      {% set featured = false %}
      {% set showPoints = false %}
      {% include "components/certification-card.njk" %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
